https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/prophet/alikckkmddkoooodkchoheabgakpopmg - Prophet - reveals more information about people. It uses an advanced engine to predict the most likely email combination for a given person based on name, company and other social data. Then, Prophet verifies the generated email to make sure it is correct and deliverable.
http://www.osintbrowser.com/ - OSINT browser extension - contains a lot of useful links, including ones for email search and verification. Compatible with Firefox and Chrome.
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/linkedin-sales-navigator/hihakjfhbmlmjdnnhegiciffjplmdhin - LinkedIn Sales Navigator - plugin for Chrome that shows associated Twitter account and rich LinkedIn profile data directly in Gmail.
